summary: A hero's dwelling with a pool and living space spread over several areas.
descriptionHtml:
[img]https://staticdelivery.nexusmods.com/mods/110/images/74308-0-1458482787.png[/img]
[color=#b6d7a8]Credit to [color=#d5a6bd][b]Jokerine[/b][/color] for the Forever Free! logo, download from [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/newvegas/mods/58832/?]here.[/url][/color]


[color=#b6d7a8][size=3]A hero's dwelling with a pool, living space spread over several areas like:
- Entrance from the back of the Talos statue.
-Livingroom with entrance to the roof to watch the Whiterun citylife
-Connected to an INN through the pool area.
-Entrance to an exterior roof and the main tower from the INN.
-Checked with TES5Edit.

Contributors, thanks to -
The Lute player, [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/58670/?]Tania the Hermit[/url] by [b]Kasprutz - Magnificat - Aryes Grace.[/b]
Skyrim version of [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/22018/?]"New Plants"[/url] by [b]Tamira.[/b]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/47376/?]UNP Minidresses Collection[/url] by [b]Tiwa44[/b].
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/20415/?]UNP Mashup Compilation[/url] by [b]Brokefoot.[/b]

This mod also works [u]without[/u] Tropical Skyrim.

Thanks to Bethesda Softworks for creating wonderous games.
Thanks to my friends on the nexusmods.
[/size][/color]
author: fredlaus
